128
01:31:30,138 --> 01:31:35,305
So, this is a new awareness,

129
01:31:35,555 --> 01:31:39,638
a new dimension, which manifests within us.

130
01:31:46,013 --> 01:31:49,555
And it takes us much beyond mental activity,

131
01:31:49,721 --> 01:31:53,721
