173
01:36:57,222 --> 01:37:00,555
So one has to be humble.

174
01:37:04,013 --> 01:37:08,595
If you are arrogant about it, your own Kundalini won’t rise.

175
01:37:16,805 --> 01:37:19,805
Moreover

176
01:37:21,055 --> 01:37:25,263
this Kundalini knows all about you.

177
01:37:29,472 --> 01:37:32,472
